{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "track-io-api-collection",
		"name": "Track.IO Backend API",
		"description": "Complete API collection for Track.IO Backend Receptor application. This collection includes all endpoints for managing areas, departments, devices, device signals, raw signals and measurements.\n\n## Base URL\nDefault: `http://localhost:3000`\n\n## Features\n- **Areas Management**: CRUD operations for areas\n- **Departments Management**: CRUD operations for departments\n- **Devices Management**: CRUD operations for devices\n- **Device Signals Management**: CRUD operations for device signals\n- **Raw Signals**: Process and retrieve raw signal data\n- **Raw Measurements**: Process and retrieve raw measurement data\n\n## Authentication\nCurrently no authentication is required.\n\n## Response Format\nAll responses follow this structure:\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Operation description\",\n  \"data\": {},\n  \"total\": 0,\n  \"pagination\": {\n    \"limit\": 10,\n    \"offset\": 0,\n    \"total\": 0\n  }\n}\n```",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "track-io-backend"
	},
